---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = "September 15, 2023";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - StoryBlog">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <article class="prose lg:prose-xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-purple-600 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          At StoryBlog, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, 
          use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you visit our website.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2">Personal Information</h3>
        <p>We may collect personal information that you voluntarily provide, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Name and email address when you create an account</li>
          <li>Profile information you provide</li>
          <li>Comments and interactions on our platform</li>
          <li>Payment information when purchasing premium content</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-purple-800 mb-2 mt-4">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p>When you visit our site, we automatically collect:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Device information</li>
          <li>Log and usage data</li>
          <li>Location information</li>
          <li>Cookies and tracking technologies</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Providing and maintaining our services</li>
          <li>Personalizing your experience</li>
          <li>Processing your transactions</li>
          <li>Communicating with you</li>
          <li>Analyzing usage patterns</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Data Protection</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational security measures to protect your 
          personal information. However, no electronic transmission over the internet can be 
          guaranteed to be 100% secure.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-purple-900 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:privacy@storyblog.com" class="text-purple-600 hover:text-purple-900">
            privacy@storyblog.com
          </a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </article>
  </main>
</Layout>